  }
```

### ‚ú® Features

- Real-time TON wallet balance fetching.
- Live cryptocurrency price lookup.
- Instant coin description extraction.
- Fast and lightweight scraping.
- get **transactions** of Wallet.
- No API keys or authentication needed.
- Working in Terminal.


